<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_ba56a6994882.aspx"><b>匪风</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonba56a6994882">
<p>匪风发兮，匪车偈兮。顾瞻周道，中心怛兮。<br />匪风飘兮，匪车嘌兮。顾瞻周道，中心吊兮。<br />谁能亨鱼？溉之釜鬵。谁将西归？怀之好音。</p>
